    • Method Detail

      • getType

        default GenericType<Integer> getType()
        Specified by:
        getType in interface ReadableProperty<Number>
        Returns:
        the type of the property value. Please note that the generic signature of this method is returning the type GenericType<? extends V> instead of GenericType <V> because JavaFx is binding the type Number for all numeric properties while e.g. IntegerProperty should be able to return GenericType<Integer> what is compatible with GenericType<? extends Number>.
